title: Aruba Networks Wireless LAN Controller (WLC): Connected WLAN Accesspoints
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/aruba
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check automatically detects all provisioned accesspoints of an
 Aruba Networks WLAN Controller which are up.
 Moreover the check reports the accesspoint group and system location if available.
 If an accesspoint goes down, the checks triggers a CRITICAL state.
 If the accespoint is inactive, the check reports a WARN state.
 If both cases appear then the worst case will be reported.
 Otherwise the check is OK.

item:
 The accesspoint name.

inventory:
 One service for each access point is created.

